metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Birds to be taken only with bow and arrow or certain type gun; plugging of gun; lights prohibited.
metadata.archived-history: Repealed 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 38, sec. 30. -- Amended 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 200, sec. 43. -- Amended 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 84, sec. 12. -- Amended 1944 Ky.
